214
00:12:42,170 --> 00:12:43,590
[Luo Wenqian,
putra kedua keluarga Luo]

215
00:12:42,270 --> 00:12:43,670
Tidak diperbolehkan menggunakan kredit.

216
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:44,790
Lihat.

217
00:12:44,790 --> 00:12:45,690
Ia pemberani dan terampil dalam pertempuran.

218
00:12:45,690 --> 00:12:47,480
Tim tersebut telah memenangkan 18 pertandingan berturut-turut di sana.

219
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:48,270
Ini...

220
00:12:48,270 --> 00:12:49,000
Saya punya uang.

221
00:12:51,750 --> 00:12:52,840
Tuliskan semuanya.

222
00:12:53,150 --> 00:12:53,870
Ayo cepat.

223
00:12:54,120 --> 00:12:54,720
Jixiang.

224
00:12:55,750 --> 00:12:57,790
Ayah semakin lama semakin
